<taxonomicName box="[500,590,1039,1060]" class="Insecta" family="Hydrophilidae" genus="Armostus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="100" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="nigricans">
<emphasis box="[500,590,1039,1060]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="100">nigricans</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is derived from ‘‘nigric‾ans’’ in Latin, meaning blackish.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
